    "long_instructions": "#### Recreate This Timeline\r\nChloe is working with another artist to create a new song. Her job is to make the beginning portion of the song before the beat drops. Here partner gave her this timeline to recreate. Use the sounds you have been given and code a song that matches the timeline below. \r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/41449167c6868065c171234b4507e788-image-1741889152965.05.48 AM.png)\r\n\r\nNeed help? Listen to the song in the media player. \r\n",
